# 2. Jenkins Declarative Pipeline

## Jenkinsfile

```groovy
pipeline {
    agent any

    stages {

        stage('Checkout') {
            steps {
                git branch: 'main',
                url: 'https://github.com/company/app.git'
            }
        }

        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                sh 'mvn clean package'
            }
        }

        stage('Test') {
            steps {
                sh 'mvn test'
            }
        }

        stage('Deploy') {
            steps {
                sh './deploy.sh'
            }
        }
    }
}
```

---

# 3. Scripted Pipeline

```groovy
node {

    stage('Build') {
        sh 'mvn clean package'
    }

    stage('Test') {
        sh 'mvn test'
    }

    stage('Deploy') {
        sh './deploy.sh'
    }
}
```

---

# 4. Jenkins Agents

Master delegates builds to agents.

```groovy
pipeline {

 agent {
   label 'linux-agent'
 }

 stages {

   stage('Build'){
      steps{
         sh 'mvn clean package'
      }
   }

 }
}
```

