# 6. SonarQube Integration

### Jenkins Stage

```groovy
stage('Sonar Scan') {

 steps {

  sh '''
  mvn sonar:sonar \
  -Dsonar.projectKey=myapp \
  -Dsonar.host.url=http://sonarqube:9000 \
  -Dsonar.login=$SONAR_TOKEN
  '''
 }
}
```

---

### Quality Gate

```groovy
stage('Quality Gate') {

 steps {

  timeout(time: 10, unit: 'MINUTES') {

   waitForQualityGate abortPipeline: true

  }
 }
}
```

