# 10. Parallel Pipeline Execution

```groovy
stage('Parallel Tests') {

 parallel {

   stage('Unit Test') {
      steps {
         sh 'mvn test'
      }
   }

   stage('Security Test') {
      steps {
         sh 'trivy image app'
      }
   }

 }
}
```

