# 2. Terraform State Management

## Remote State (S3)

```hcl
terraform {
  backend "s3" {
    bucket = "terraform-state-prod"
    key    = "prod/terraform.tfstate"
    region = "ap-south-1"
  }
}
```

---

## State Locking (DynamoDB)

```hcl
terraform {
  backend "s3" {

    bucket         = "terraform-state-prod"
    key            = "prod/state.tfstate"
    region         = "ap-south-1"
    dynamodb_table = "terraform-locks"

  }
}
```

Benefits:

* Team collaboration
* Prevent concurrent changes
* Centralized state

