# 9. Amazon CloudWatch

## English

Monitoring service.

Tracks:

* CPU
* Memory
* Disk
* Logs

Alarm Example:

```text
CPU > 80%
Send Email
```

---

## Hinglish

CloudWatch AWS ka monitoring tool hai.

Server ki health monitor karta hai.

---

# 10. AWS CLI

## English

Command-line interface for AWS.

List Buckets:

```bash
aws s3 ls
```

---

## Hinglish

AWS ko terminal se manage karne ke liye use hota hai.

---

# 11. Route 53

## English

DNS service.

Example:

```text
example.com
     |
     v
 ALB
```

Routing Policies:

* Simple
* Weighted
* Latency
* Failover

---

## Hinglish

Route53 domain ko AWS resources se connect karta hai.

---

# 12. CloudFront

## English

CDN service.

Caches content at edge locations.

Benefits:

* Faster website
* Reduced latency

---

## Hinglish

CloudFront images aur static files ko user ke nearest location se serve karta hai.

---

# 13. AWS Lambda

## English

Serverless service.

Run code without managing servers.

Example:

```python
def lambda_handler(event, context):
    return {
      "statusCode": 200
    }
```

---

## Hinglish

Server manage nahi karna padta.

Sirf code upload karo aur Lambda execute karega.

---

# 14. IAM (Identity and Access Management)

## English

Controls permissions.

Components:

* Users
* Groups
* Roles
* Policies

Example Policy:

```json
{
 "Effect":"Allow",
 "Action":"s3:*",
 "Resource":"*"
}
```

---

## Hinglish

IAM decide karta hai kaun kya access kar sakta hai.

Example:
Developer ko EC2 access mile.
Finance team ko na mile.

